  "remarks": "Passport no: Iraq number A4059346, issued on 29 May 2013, issued in Baghdad, Iraq (expires on 27 May 2021). National identification no: a) Iraq national identification card 00405771, issued on 20 May 2013, issued in Iraq (name in Arabic script: عمر محمود إرحيم الفياض) b) Iraq Certificate of Iraqi Nationality 540763, issued on 13 Feb. 1984 (name in Arabic script: عمر محمود إرحيم). Financial facilitator for Islamic State in Iraq and the Levant, listed as Al-Qaida in Iraq (QDe.115). Director of Al-Kawthar Money Exchange (QDe.157). Physical description: sex: male, hair colour: black; height: 175 cm. Speaks Arabic. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021)\nwas concluded on 30 October 2023.; Listing: Listed on: 6 Mar. 2018",
